hopobject.body: How do you spell that? difference between prescription drugs and nonprescription drugs He helped create the Southwest Climate Science Center at the University of Arizona and is part of the Safe Climate Caucus, a group of House members committed to raising the profile of global warming. In May, he organized a letter to President Barack Obama signed by 30 members of Congress urging the president to reject the Keystone XL pipeline because of climate concerns.
